# Biomarker Screening: Preliminary Funding Distribution

## Purpose

A preliminary look at where and how NIH biomarker-related funding is distributed,
based on keyword screening of ~{{ "{:,}".format(summary.total_grants) }} grants (FY{{ summary.year_range[0] }}–{{ summary.year_range[1] }}).
This is Phase 1 of a two-phase pipeline. Phase 2 uses LLM grading to evaluate
grants through a methodological lens about biomarker R&D with long-horizon decision
making in mind (see `data/RUBRIC.md`), rather than relying on keywords.

